OL,3,CKing to broadcast Christmas message
OL,4,Cfrom outside Royal residence for
OL,5,Csecond time
OL,7,FThe King has recorded his Christmas
OL,8,FBroadcast outside a Royal residence
OL,9,Ffor the second time in his reign,
OL,10,Fchoosing the historic site of
OL,11,FWestminster Abbey.
OL,13,FThe message, which will be broadcast
OL,14,Fon television and radio at 3pm on
OL,15,FChristmas Day, was filmed in the Lady
OL,16,FChapel at the far eastern end of the
OL,17,FRoyal Peculiar.
OL,19,FWestminster Abbey has a long history
OL,20,Fas a site of pilgrimage which aligns
OL,21,Fwith a key theme of the message.
