OL,7,FPilgrims visit each year to remember
OL,8,Fthe life and legacy of Edward the
OL,9,FConfessor whose shrine lies at the
OL,10,Fheart of the Abbey.
OL,12,FEdward, who reigned for 24 years
OL,13,Fbefore dying in 1066, was said to be a
OL,14,Fmonk-like monarch believed to have the
OL,15,Fpower to heal and was canonised by
OL,16,FPope Alexander III in 1161.
