OL,3,CKing to broadcast Christmas message
OL,4,Cfrom outside Royal residence for
OL,5,Csecond time
OL,7,FIt is the fourth Christmas Broadcast
OL,8,Fof the King's reign, and the second
OL,9,Fstaged outside a royal residence after
OL,10,Fit was filmed at the Fitzrovia Chapel
OL,11,Fin London last year.
OL,13,FThe chapel, which was once at the
OL,14,Fheart of the now demolished Middlesex
OL,15,FHospital, was chosen because it has a
OL,16,Fconnection to health, is a community
OL,17,Fspace and is a place of spiritual
OL,18,Fsolace and reflection.
